author: Benjamin Neo
text:
Have been training here for over 2 years, and I would highly recommend this AF outlet. Although the space is a little small, this AF outlet offers excellent facilities and gym equipment, while having members of staff that consistently ensures the cleanliness of the gym space and gym equipment.

Unlike other gyms, the members of staff at this AF outlet engages both newcomers and seasoned AF members with a friendly, encouraging, and positive attitude. Should you have any questions or issues, the members of staff are quick to respond and resolve them.

Small outlet but surprisingly well equipped. At least 1 machine for every muscle group and free weights go up to 50?kg IIRC. 2 squat racks, 1 smith machine & 2 benches. At the time I‚Äôm posting this it‚Äôs right as their club refresh is starting. Can‚Äôt wait to see the new look.

No deadlift platform due to space constraint but a good sized functional area + equipment.

Convenient for me to get a workout in as it‚Äôs nearby home. Though I‚Äôm unsure of how bad the crowd gets on weekday evening as I prefer to frequent on weekend mornings (~7am) and it‚Äôll be quite empty.

The staff are also all friendly and greet you with a smile as you come in. I really appreciated it when I was first starting my fitness journey and made me feel secure enough to sign membership here :)

author: Michele Chang
text:
Anytime Fitness Tampines West CC is a convenient and accessible gym located in Tampines, Singapore. It offers a range of fitness facilities and services, making it a popular choice for individuals looking to stay active and fit.

The gym is well-equipped with a variety of exercise machines and equipment, catering to different workout preferences and fitness levels. Whether you prefer cardio exercises, strength training, or group fitness classes, Anytime Fitness Tampines West CC has something for everyone. The gym is clean and well-maintained, providing a comfortable and safe environment for workouts.

One of the key advantages of Anytime Fitness is its 24/7 access, allowing members to exercise at their convenience. This flexibility is particularly beneficial for individuals with busy schedules or those who prefer to work out during off-peak hours. The gym also offers secure access, ensuring members can work out with peace of mind.

author: Marvin Woo
text: I love this place. It's small, old & run down. The toilets are smelly & dirty. BUT this community centre leads the way in linking up residents by having lotsa cool & fun activities organised frequently. There are movie nights, EPL nights, fringe activities, lots of freebies like snacks, balloons sculptures, fun photo-taking sessions, plus many more activities to keep families & kids engaged & occupied. Great!!!

The membership fees are affordable, making it a great option for those on a budget. Overall, Anytime Fitness Tampines West Community Club is a great choice for those looking for a convenient and affordable gym in the Tampines area

author: swee geok neo
text: Community centers are government-run institutions managed by local communities and have neighborhood committees. They disseminate information to the government and to all neighborhood committee chairpersons in the area. During neighborhood committee meetings, the chairpersons present information to the committee members. This information helps residents understand government initiatives and gathers public information to inform the government, helping them understand the dynamics of residents' lives. They also organize activities to engage and inform residents.
